title: War of the Roses: She Found a Strange Pair of Underwear
description: Miranda has been with her boyfriend Troy for 12 years.  He had an affair once before but she took him back.  Now she found a pair of his underwear with a strange design on it that were clearly new, and something he would never buy.  Where did he get the underwear from, or WHO did he get them from?
